# Cloudflare Pages redirects and routing

# Redirect www to non-www (canonical domain)
https://www.z3connect.com/* https://z3connect.com/:splat 301!

# Hybrid Routing: Redirect static paths to React app where needed
/vlogs /blogs 301
/vlogs.html /blogs 301
/contact.html /contact 301
/portfolio.html /work.html 301

# SPA Fallback for React (Blogs/Contact)
/blogs/* /blogs 200
/contact/* /contact 200
/admin/* /admin 200
